javadoc:
Dialog showing all users associated with a repository and those with 
 access to the current shared project. Users with admin rights can use
 this dialog to edit user permissions.

methods.name: <init>

params.name: knownUsers
params.comment: list of all users in the repository

params.name: allowEditing
params.comment: if true, widgets for adding/removing users will be available
